<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>السَّبَب/ع،<span class="c5"> الأَسْبَاب/ع:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">مِنْ جَرَّاءِ كَذَا وَكَذَا:</span> أَيْ بِسَبَبِ كَذَا وَكَذَا،<span class="c5"> وَمِنهُ هَذَا الحَدِيث:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
